                 SAXException,

        Creates a new PvKParams object from the specified XML file.
        Parameters:
        paramsFilePath - The path to the XML file to read the parameters from.
        Throws:
        IOException - If an error occurs while reading the file.
        SAXException - If any XML parse error occurs.
        SpecificationNotMetException - If the XML file does not meet the schema's requirements.

      • PvKParams

        public PvKParams()
        Creates a new empty PvKParams object that has to be filled via Parameters' methods. When all parameters are set, the method populatePublicFields() has to be called to make the public fields of this class usable.
